Document: RDTextureFormat
Path: godot/classes/class_rdtextureformat.rst
Summary: Defines texture formats for the RenderingDevice.

RDTextureFormat is an enum that defines texture formats for the RenderingDevice. These formats specify how texture data is stored in memory, including its pixel layout, bit depth, and channel order.

